  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2615510/extras/e1f4aac50bb1e966559fb9e15603995c.avif?t=1728316361\" width=574 height=121 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Winter is here!!! Let's play!!!</strong></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Grab your winter gear and a blanket to enjoy a new SQUARE WORD episode!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2615510/extras/11c894850c8bd358f8b79fc9cd2bd9e1.webp?t=1728316361\" width=600 height=5 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>ALEX, the little penguin,</strong> is very happy to start a new adventure with you!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2615510/extras/e1566e66c2db5755f408b2e913f31422.webp?t=1728316361\" width=13 height=13 /></span> <strong>Four very cool themes: Christmas - Cold - Toyz - Cozy House</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2615510/extras/e1566e66c2db5755f408b2e913f31422.webp?t=1728316361\" width=13 height=13 /></span> 140+ words to find.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2615510/extras/e1566e66c2db5755f408b2e913f31422.webp?t=1728316361\" width=13 height=13 /></span> Handcrafted grids.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2615510/extras/e1566e66c2db5755f408b2e913f31422.webp?t=1728316361\" width=13 height=13 /></span> Daily challenge.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2615510/extras/e1566e66c2db5755f408b2e913f31422.webp?t=1728316361\" width=13 height=13 /></span> 4 difficulties (easy to very hard).</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2615510/extras/e1566e66c2db5755f408b2e913f31422.webp?t=1728316361\" width=13 height=13 /></span> Difficulty increasing gradually.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2615510/extras/e1566e66c2db5755f408b2e913f31422.webp?t=1728316361\" width=13 height=13 /></span> Letter & word hints.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2615510/extras/e1566e66c2db5755f408b2e913f31422.webp?t=1728316361\" width=13 height=13 /></span> Collect Stamps with extra objectives and receive rewards!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2615510/extras/e1566e66c2db5755f408b2e913f31422.webp?t=1728316361\" width=13 height=13 /></span> Additional songs.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Are you ready?</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2615510/extras/86c011db27ae971b73858d42b8beb21a.avif?t=1728316361\" width=574 height=252 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2615510/extras/11c894850c8bd358f8b79fc9cd2bd9e1.webp?t=1728316361\" width=600 heigh